OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FWicked star Cynthia Erivo and former
OL,7,FEngland footballer Tony Adams will be
OL,8,Famong the thousands to race in the TCS
OL,9,FLondon Marathon on Sunday in what is
OL,10,Fset to be its biggest year yet.
OL,12,FRecord-breaking numbers are expected
OL,13,Fat the start line in Greenwich, with
OL,14,Fmore than 59,000 people gearing up to
OL,15,Frace in warm sunshine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
