FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FTemperatures are forecast to reach the
OL,7,Fhigh teens, with participants taking
OL,8,Fon the 26.2-mile course advised to
OL,9,Fstay hydrated ahead of the marathon
OL,10,Fand wear lightweight clothing on the
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,FLast year, the event broke the
OL,14,FGuinness World Record (GWR) for the
OL,15,Fmost finishers in a marathon, with
OL,16,F56,640 participants making it to the
OL,17,Fend ` a record organisers hope to beat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FAround 55.7% of participants
OL,7,Fregistered for this year's race are
OL,8,Fmale while some 44.2% are female and
OL,9,F0.15% non-binary.
OL,11,FIt is set to be the most inclusive
OL,12,FLondon Marathon in history, with more
OL,13,Fthan 1,900 people with a disability
OL,14,Fregistered to take part, organisers
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FOscar-nominee Erivo, who ran in 2022,
OL,18,Fwill race for The King's Trust and
OL,19,FShameless Fund while former Arsenal
OL,20,Fcaptain Adams is racing for the first
OL,21,Ftime, in support of the Forward Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
