PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FSpeaking on the Nobody Asked Us with
OL,7,FDes and Kara podcast on Friday, Erivo
OL,8,Fsaid: "A win is if we get there and
OL,9,Fit's less than 3.35 (her 2022 run
OL,10,Ftime). If we get 3.20, that's the win,
OL,11,Fthat is the practical side.
OL,13,F"The other side is actually getting to
OL,14,Fthis weekend and getting to the start
OL,15,Fline tomorrow is a huge win, because
OL,16,Fit's been a really long, wild process."
OL,18,FShe added: "The fact that we've got
OL,19,Fhere and, come rain or shine, I'm
OL,20,Fgetting to the finish line... that
OL,21,Fwill be the win to me."
