OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FAmong those to race costumed is Jordan
OL,7,FAdams, who plans to strap a fridge to
OL,8,Fhis back "because we are all carrying
OL,9,Fsomething. And we don't have to carry
OL,10,Fit alone," he said in a statement
OL,11,Freleased through mental health charity
OL,12,FMind.
OL,14,FMr Adams was diagnosed with early-
OL,15,Fonset frontotemporal dementia in 2018,
OL,16,Fa disease which his mother died of two
OL,17,Fyears before.
OL,26,@pD@JOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
