OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FElite runners for the men's field
OL,7,Finclude Kenya's Sebastian Sawe, who
OL,8,Fplaced first in his category last
OL,9,Fyear, while Rafael Botello Jimenez,
OL,10,Ffrom Spain, will be among the top
OL,11,Fparticipants in the men's wheelchair
OL,12,Ffield.
OL,14,FLast year's fastest woman, Tigst
OL,15,FAssefa, from Ethiopia, will hope to
OL,16,Fretain her crown, while Mauritia's
OL,17,FNoemi Alphonse will be among the top
OL,18,Fcompetitors in the women's wheelchair
OL,19,Ffield.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
