FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FThe oldest participants to cross the
OL,7,Fstart line will be Harry Newton, 88,
OL,8,Fand Maria Rivera, 86.
OL,10,FCelebrating their 18th birthdays on
OL,11,Fmarathon day, Olivier Smythe, Khadija
OL,12,FKhalfaoui and Molly Bull-Diamond will
OL,13,Fbe the youngest racers.
OL,15,FSome 76 participants are hoping to
OL,16,Fbreak 73 GWRs, including Jennifer
OL,17,FFerris, 40, who will attempt to run
OL,18,Fthe world's fastest marathon with a
OL,19,Fdouble mastectomy in aid of Breast
OL,20,FCancer Now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
