PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FMark Goulder, 35, hopes to break the
OL,7,Frecord for the fastest marathon
OL,8,Fblindfolded (tethered), inspired by
OL,9,Fhis younger brother Bobby, who was
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with Stargardt's disease ` a
OL,11,Frare, genetic eye disorder that causes
OL,12,Fprogressive vision loss.
OL,14,FRoyal Marines Commando veteran Simon
OL,15,FFannon will attempt the record for
OL,16,Flongest scarf knitted while running a
OL,17,Fmarathon while Ben Spencer, 52, will
OL,18,Fattempt the fastest marathon in a non-
OL,19,Fracing wheelchair (male).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
