FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777255442
OL,3,CCynthia Erivo and Tony Adams among
OL,4,Cmore than 59,000 to run London Marathon
OL,6,FLast year, the event raised a record
OL,7,F#87.3 million, bringing the cumulative
OL,8,Ftotal raised since the first race in
OL,9,F1981 to #1.4 billion, according to
OL,10,Forganisers.
OL,12,FMarie Curie, the event's charity of
OL,13,Fthe year for 2026, hopes to raise #2
OL,14,Fmillion to fund care for those at the
OL,15,Fend of their lives and support for
OL,16,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,18,FThis year, the event's estimated
OL,19,F800,000 spectators will be encouraged
OL,20,Fto sign up to give blood as part of
OL,21,Fthe Blood, Sweat and Cheers campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
